WEBVTT

00:01.720 --> 00:02.480
I don't know

00:10.960 --> 00:12.360
I don't care about the realm

00:12.880 --> 00:13.720
Or going north

00:14.720 --> 00:16.040
That's for you to consider

00:17.320 --> 00:18.480
But when you married me

00:18.480 --> 00:19.120
You promised me

00:20.040 --> 00:21.240
When we return to the north

00:21.720 --> 00:23.320
You'd take me to Bashang to break willow branches

00:23.760 --> 00:24.960
And return to Yong'an to admire flowers

00:25.440 --> 00:25.960
Alright

00:27.160 --> 00:27.960
How about

00:28.120 --> 00:29.800
I write you an IOU

00:30.600 --> 00:31.280
Just write

00:31.920 --> 00:32.960
Owe my wife

00:33.040 --> 00:34.320
A trip to Bashang to break willow branches

00:34.960 --> 00:36.440
And to Yong'an to admire flowers

00:40.360 --> 00:41.840
Do you know why I came to see you?

00:42.880 --> 00:43.960
What is it, my wife?

00:46.440 --> 00:47.640
If you

00:47.840 --> 00:49.160
Stay away too long

00:50.440 --> 00:52.160
I'll name the child myself

00:54.000 --> 00:54.840
What?

00:55.840 --> 00:56.640
I said

00:58.080 --> 00:59.320
You're going to be a father

01:07.160 --> 01:08.240
I'll return as soon as possible

01:09.440 --> 01:10.160
I promise
